#: code:addons/whatsapp_sign/models/sign_request.py:0
msgid ""
"All Whatsapp templates must be configured before creating the sign request."
msgstr "ແມ່ແບບ WhatsApp ທັງໝົດຕ້ອງໄດ້ຮັບການຕັ້ງຄ່າກ່ອນທີ່ຈະສ້າງຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍລາຍເຊັນ."

#. module: whatsapp_sign
#. odoo-python
